  **¬ß7 ‚Äî Composition cascade (strict)**

  SC-60 ‚Äî Mechanism(DRAFT), Effector(DRAFT), Receptor(DRAFT).
  Effector.Artifact(PROPOSED), Receptor.Artifact(PROPOSED).
