  Effector2(DRAFT): **NO-OP** (Mechanism2 not cascaded).
  Receptor2(DRAFT): **NO-OP** (Mechanism2 not cascaded).

  ====

  **¬ß11 ‚Äî Composition cascade failure blocks source**

  SC-95 ‚Äî Mechanism(ACTIVE), Effector(ACTIVE),
